to use this code, follow the steps below:

1. Create a new Spreadsheet
2. give it a name
3. Give a name to its sheet as well
4. Make table having headers as [id, first name, last name, title, message, email]
5. fill some data in these columns
6. go to the extensions >> Apps Script
7. Change the title of the project to as desired.
8. use the script file code in the code.gs file 
9. replace your spreadsheet id
10. replace your sheet name
11. Give permissions to it
12. Run and send the emails
